    "Visualization of Knowledge GraphsTo visualize the knowledge graphs, the following steps were implemented:• Graphical Representation: NetworkX was employed to create a graphical representation of the knowledge graphs.",
    "Nodes were colored differently to distinguish between entities from the two different datasets, with a unique color assigned to common entities found in both datasets.",
    "• Layout Optimization: The spring layout algorithm was used to position the nodes of the graph, aiming for a visually appealing and informative display.",
    "• Custom Adjustments: Manual adjustments were made to the node labels and legend placement to enhance clarity and prevent overlap.Each graph serves as a visual aid to better understand the complex relationships and information patterns derived from the AI's text-based responses.Figure 4 shows the knowledge representation of three Bard responses and three ChatGPT responses to each of the prompts for the question, What role do coastal ecosystems play in carbon sequestration and climate regulation?",
    "This question involves an understanding of terrestrial, marine, and climate interactions taking place in coastal ecosystems."
